title: “GET STRONG” Best Core Exercises For Kids (15 Minute Kids Workout)
description:
Today Vivien is leading a 15 Minute Kids Workout to get a strong core and body!  These are the best core exercises for kids to get better performance results! 

We hope you love these KIDS CORE EXERCISES TO GET STRONG! 

We put out new kids workouts every week - subscribe to our channel: @GVOKids
